topics
lessons

1. Tables to add:   - topics table - Store topic infomation
                    - lesson_topics table - join table connecting lessons and topics

    Associations
        Topic has_many lessons through lesson_topics
        Lesson has_many topics through lesson_topics
        LessonTopic belong_to both lesson and topic

2. Association columns required
    join table needs foreign keys lesson_id and topic_id for many_to_many relationship

3. Additional columns needed
    Topics table: title(string) to store topic names
    Rails timestamps
    Primary key

4. Table structure
    Topics Table
        id:integer (primary key)
        title: string
        created_at: datetime
        updated_at: datetime

    Lesson_Topics table
        id: integer (primary key)
        lesson_id: integer (foreign key)
        topic_id: integer (foreign key)
        created_at: datetime
        updated_at: datetime

5. Generator command
      rails generate migration create_topics
